he asked me for.

23:19.327 --> 23:21.577
The very next day.
Ten thousand dollars.

23:25.077 --> 23:26.993
How did he know that
you were seein' the woman?

23:27.118 --> 23:30.118
He stayed at the hotel
that I went to with the, uh,

23:30.243 --> 23:33.577
lady in question.
